---
title: Indian-Spiced Beyond Meat® Burgers with Sweet Potato Wedges and Cilantro Yogurt Dip
description: Shake up your at-home burger game! These Beyond Meat® burgers get a dose of sweetness from our fig spread. The gentle tartness of the yogurt dip pulls double duty: It adds a layer of flavour to the burger's spring greens and serves as a delicious dip for earthy sweet potatoes.
